for the next year.

104
00:04:29,185 --> 00:04:31,562
We will be on this ward
with real patients,

105
00:04:31,646 --> 00:04:34,023
and you will have me
in supervision as your teacher,

106
00:04:34,107 --> 00:04:35,942
your protector, your sounding board,

107
00:04:36,025 --> 00:04:38,152
your overall psych Sherpa
on this amazing journey

108
00:04:38,236 --> 00:04:39,654
