115
00:04:56,296 --> 00:04:58,589
And don't expect me
to care if your pet is sick.

116
00:04:58,673 --> 00:05:02,302
Chief Resident Walsh will field questions
and let you know when you screwed up.

117
00:05:02,385 --> 00:05:05,596
