but, uh, wasn't right for either of us.

144
00:06:34,352 --> 00:06:35,478
So I ended it.

145
00:06:36,813 --> 00:06:39,398
And now I'd like to just move on.

146
00:06:41,734 --> 00:06:45,696
Floyd, if you really care for this woman,
you should find a way to make it work.

147
00:06:47,698 --> 00:06:50,701
