149
00:06:53,538 --> 00:06:56,582
<i>-♪ And I know, I know, I know, I know ♪</i>
-[sighs]

150
00:06:56,666 --> 00:06:59,335
<i>♪ I know, I know</i>
<i>I know, I know, I know... ♪</i>

151
00:06:59,669 --> 00:07:01,129
