or my meetings anymore.

157
00:07:10,138 --> 00:07:12,223
Given that's the entirety
of my responsibilities,

158
00:07:12,306 --> 00:07:13,307
what should I focus on?

159
00:07:13,391 --> 00:07:14,600
Joy.

160
00:07:14,892 --> 00:07:16,269
I want you to focus on joy.

161
00:07:16,352 --> 00:07:17,979
Walk me through what that might look like.

162
00:07:18,062 --> 00:07:21,232
Finding it, seizing it. That's what
this new beginning is all about,

163
00:07:21,315 --> 00:07:23,776
refocusing on what truly matters.

164
00:07:23,860 --> 00:07:27,029
Re-examining our lives
to maximize the joy,

165
00:07:27,113 --> 00:07:29,115
the beauty, the people that we love,

166
00:07:29,198 --> 00:07:31,576
and nothing should distract us
from that noble goal.

167
00:07:31,659 --> 00:07:33,870
[alarm blares]

168
00:07:33,953 --> 00:07:36,622
[woman] <i>May I have your attention?</i>
<i>There is a fire in the building.</i>

169
00:07:36,706 --> 00:07:38,833
Maybe we start that joy thing tomorrow.

170
00:07:38,916 --> 00:07:40,835
-[panicked chattering]
-What the hell happened?

171
00:07:40,918 --> 00:07:46,632
