175
00:08:10,990 --> 00:08:12,408
I have thought of nothing...

176
00:08:14,076 --> 00:08:17,246
but you... and this

177
00:08:18,122 --> 00:08:19,457
for so long.

178
00:08:20,958 --> 00:08:23,961
Thought it, but didn't know how to say it.

179
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:26,380
Or maybe I was afraid to.

180
00:08:28,007 --> 00:08:31,469
And now it just feels
like I have a future again.

181
00:08:34,889 --> 00:08:35,765
With you...

182
00:08:37,683 --> 00:08:38,851
just like this.

183
00:08:41,938 --> 00:08:43,773
I should never have let you in.

184
00:08:47,568 --> 00:08:49,695
[indistinct chatter]

185
00:08:55,451 --> 00:08:58,246
Could've been worse, Dr. Goodwin.
Luckily the sprinklers got it

186
00:08:58,329 --> 00:08:59,914
before the fire got to the gas lines.

187
00:08:59,997 --> 00:09:01,457
