-Walsh, let's get her to trauma one.

223
00:10:44,894 --> 00:10:48,022
Um, Turan, can, um...
can you take over with Brandon?

224
00:10:48,105 --> 00:10:50,566
He needs
two doses of ibuprofen every five hours

225
00:10:50,650 --> 00:10:53,027
and three doses
of colchicine every eight hours.

226
00:10:53,110 --> 00:10:55,154
Write it down so he gets the timing right.

227
00:10:55,237 --> 00:10:58,407
[sighs] We're less than a year away
from needing our own selfie wing.

228
00:10:58,908 --> 00:11:00,159
[Walsh] What've you got?

229
00:11:00,743 --> 00:11:02,953
-Let's hear it, people!
-It looks like a tib-fib fracture.

230
00:11:03,037 --> 00:11:04,872
